      <title>日元强劲上涨，140 成为交易员的重要目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/-formidable-yen-rally-turns-140-into-a-big-target-for-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过 24 小时的激烈交易，日元创下了一年半多以来的最佳月度表现，Amundi 和道明证券的策略师预测日元兑美元汇率可能会升至 140。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/-formidable-yen-rally-turns-140-into-a-big-target-for-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值致日本出口商股价创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市暴跌，东证指数在全线抛售中创下2020年4月以来的最大跌幅，因为日元大幅上涨令出口商承压，央行加息拖累房地产股下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
