      <title>据报道伊朗下令实施报复性打击，油价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，伊朗已下令对以色列实施报复性打击，以报复其在以色列领土上杀害一名哈马斯领导人，随后油价在周三飙升之后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股市抛售导致全球股市涨势停滞，日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市创 2020 年以来最大跌幅，日元上涨，因交易员准备迎接日本央行进一步加息。受中东紧张局势影响，油价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
